article.headline: Western Illinois 59, Centenary 68
article.story: SHREVEPORT, La, (AP) -- Fred Oguns scored 17 points and grabbed 10 rebounds as Western Illinois beat Centenary 68-59 on Saturday. Western Illinois (7-15, 3-8 Mid Continent), also got 20 points from Sammy Hunter. Western Illinois shot 46 percent from the field -- 43 percent from 3-point distance. Centenary was led by Eric Holmes' 13 points. Larry Logan chipped in 11 points for the Gents. Centenary (4-18, 2-9) shot 39 percent from the field and made only 4 of 19 3-points attempts. Western Illinois was up 32-27 at halftime.
